title: Office 2010 ProPlus English (x64) March 13, 2018
description:
* Release Info

- Language: English (en-US)
- Channel: Volume License
- Version: 14.0.7194.5000
- Proofing Tools: English, French, Spanish
- Updated: March 13, 2018
- 64-bit version runs on 64-bit systems only
- OS: Windows 10/8.1/8,7 SP1 + Server/Server 2012 R2/2012/Server 2008 R2

* Bonus folder

- Previous versions uninstallers (Office 2007, 2003)
- KMSpico 10.2.0 + Microsoft Toolkit 2.6.3 Final
- Classic Menu for Office 5.85 (adds Office 2003 type toolbars and menus to Office 2013)
- Office Tab Enterprise 9.81 (adds tabs to Word, PowerPoint, and Excel documents)
- ShellNewHandler (easily remove New Microsoft_xxxx document from Windows Explorer context menu)
- Visual Studio for Office Runtime (folder KB3001652) - required update

* Installation

- Mount / burn / extract ISO file
- Install Office components
- Activate using KMSpico (recommended) / Microsoft Toolkit
- Install Visual Studio for Office Runtime and Security update for Word Viewer (folder Mandatory updates)

* Optional

- Install Classic Menu for Office / Office Tab
- Run ShellNewHandler (easily remove New Microsoft_xxxx document from Windows Explorer context menu)
